1
00:00:35,966 --> 00:00:38,633
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,633 --> 00:00:41,200
=Episode 30=

3
00:00:41,733 --> 00:00:43,000
A prince of the blood,

4
00:00:43,866 --> 00:00:45,233
scrambling for profit with commoners.

5
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:46,633
How impressive.

6
00:00:47,166 --> 00:00:49,166
Your Majesty, the Crown Prince
has just been named.

7
00:00:49,266 --> 00:00:50,300
The realm has only just settled.

8
00:00:50,566 --> 00:00:53,166
I fear someone may use this
to stir up trouble

9
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,400
and force our son to leave for his fief.

10
00:00:55,066 --> 00:00:56,100
Shouldn't he go?

11
00:00:56,733 --> 00:00:59,166
Your Majesty, if someone at court

12
00:00:59,366 --> 00:01:00,400
uses this to cause more unrest

13
00:01:00,533 --> 00:01:01,466
and attack our son,

14
00:01:01,766 --> 00:01:02,833
what are we to do?

15
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:04,533
Yes. Father.

16
00:01:05,233 --> 00:01:05,833
Son.

17
00:01:06,233 --> 00:01:07,600
Tell me the truth.

18
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,100
Behind my back,

19
00:01:10,833 --> 00:01:11,900
have you been building factions

20
00:01:12,433 --> 00:01:13,700
and reaching for court power?

21
00:01:15,366 --> 00:01:16,566
I would never dare.

22
00:01:16,933 --> 00:01:19,500
Not even if my life depended on it.

23
00:01:21,233 --> 00:01:22,000
If you haven't,

24
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:23,633
there is nothing to fear.

25
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:30,066
Go to the Cabinet.

26
00:01:30,266 --> 00:01:31,433
When you see the Grand Secretary,

27
00:01:32,333 --> 00:01:33,433
deliver my order.

28
00:01:34,066 --> 00:01:35,166
The Meizhen House case

29
00:01:36,266 --> 00:01:37,466
must be handled with care.

30
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,800
No one is to use it as a pretext

31
00:01:40,266 --> 00:01:41,300
to implicate half the court.

32
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:47,700
Grand Secretary.

33
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,200
What is that supposed to mean?

34
00:01:49,433 --> 00:01:52,200
We only charge Gao Tianxi
with detaining a female Jinyiwei

35
00:01:52,433 --> 00:01:53,533
and drop everything else?

36
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,666
More than half the court

37
00:01:57,066 --> 00:01:58,133
is standing behind Meizhen House.

38
00:01:58,533 --> 00:02:01,300
We have witnesses and evidence.

39
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,433
Your evidence is just
a few account books.

40
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:05,800
Besides the two female Jinyiwei
under you,

41
00:02:06,766 --> 00:02:08,533
do you have any other witnesses?

42
00:02:21,833 --> 00:02:22,500
(Hua.)

43
00:02:23,266 --> 00:02:23,800
(Hua.)

44
00:02:26,366 --> 00:02:27,066
(There is blood here.)

45
00:02:27,266 --> 00:02:28,200
(Follow the trail.)

46
00:02:31,566 --> 00:02:32,066
(Empty.)

47
00:02:36,833 --> 00:02:38,000
(Hua. Hua.)

48
00:02:49,233 --> 00:02:49,633
(Hua.)

49
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:52,666
(I already told the Commander.)

50
00:02:54,333 --> 00:02:56,333
(You have left the past behind.)

51
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:58,766
(You are a true Jinyiwei now.)

52
00:02:59,266 --> 00:02:59,933
The medicine is here.

53
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:01,500
Here.

54
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,433
How is Hua?

55
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:12,066
You all can leave.

56
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:13,600
I will stay with her

57
00:03:14,766 --> 00:03:15,866
and make sure nothing happens to her.

58
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,433
Open the door.

59
00:03:20,533 --> 00:03:21,300
Gao Tianxi.

60
00:03:22,033 --> 00:03:22,900
I will kill you!

61
00:03:23,033 --> 00:03:23,600
What are you doing?

62
00:03:24,033 --> 00:03:24,466
Stop!

63
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:26,800
Put the blade down.

64
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:29,233
Shen Bingfan.

65
00:03:29,233 --> 00:03:30,433
You think you can kill me?

66
00:03:30,433 --> 00:03:31,000
What a joke!

67
00:03:35,433 --> 00:03:36,133
Shen Bingfan.

68
00:03:36,766 --> 00:03:37,700
I knew you would do this.

69
00:03:39,066 --> 00:03:40,000
If you kill him,

70
00:03:40,733 --> 00:03:41,566
you become no better than him.

71
00:03:42,066 --> 00:03:42,333
Give it to me.

72
00:03:44,166 --> 00:03:44,666
Give it to me.

73
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,700
Bingfan, listen to Mr. Lu for now.

74
00:03:50,366 --> 00:03:50,766
Bingfan.

75
00:03:51,333 --> 00:03:52,033
Leave this to me.

76
00:03:54,233 --> 00:03:54,800
Come on, Bingfan.

77
00:04:03,366 --> 00:04:04,066
They are gone.

78
00:04:04,066 --> 00:04:05,233
Now get out.

79
00:04:05,233 --> 00:04:05,933
Get out!

80
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:09,300
Gao Tianxi.

81
00:04:09,933 --> 00:04:10,466
What is this?

82
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,833
You deserve to die.

83
00:04:13,533 --> 00:04:13,966
What?

84
00:04:14,166 --> 00:04:14,833
You deserve to die.

85
00:04:15,433 --> 00:04:16,200
What is this thing?

86
00:04:16,233 --> 00:04:16,833
You deserve to die!

87
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,833
What is this?

88
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
Why does it taste sweet?

89
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,266
Rats!

90
00:04:30,066 --> 00:04:30,466
Rats!

91
00:04:36,933 --> 00:04:37,466
Help!

92
00:04:40,566 --> 00:04:41,133
Help!

93
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,666
We searched all of Meizhen House,

94
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:53,000
every last inch,

95
00:04:53,433 --> 00:04:54,966
but found no trace of Leng Xin.

96
00:04:55,666 --> 00:04:56,733
Tell me.

97
00:04:57,266 --> 00:04:58,200
Could Gao Tianxi

98
00:04:58,933 --> 00:05:00,133
be Leng Xin himself?

99
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:02,200
We have all fought Leng Xin before.

100
00:05:03,266 --> 00:05:04,166
He is short,

101
00:05:04,333 --> 00:05:05,200
thin,

102
00:05:05,866 --> 00:05:07,233
and Gao Tianxi is big and tall.

103
00:05:07,766 --> 00:05:08,166
It's not him.

104
00:05:09,433 --> 00:05:10,633
Gao Tianxi is skilled,

105
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,066
but he is no match
for Young Master Chang.

106
00:05:12,733 --> 00:05:13,566
Leng Xin's skill

107
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,966
is beyond all of us.

108
00:05:17,566 --> 00:05:18,266
Could it be

109
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:20,366
that before we sealed off Meizhen House,

110
00:05:21,233 --> 00:05:22,466
Leng Xin had already slipped away?

111
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,266
It seems

112
00:05:23,733 --> 00:05:26,066
we must uncover every secret
in Meizhen House

113
00:05:27,066 --> 00:05:28,133
before we can find Leng Xin.

114
00:05:38,733 --> 00:05:40,466
Hua, you are awake.

115
00:05:41,066 --> 00:05:41,266
You...

116
00:05:41,366 --> 00:05:42,100
How do you feel?

117
00:05:42,233 --> 00:05:43,100
Any discomfort?

118
00:05:44,266 --> 00:05:44,933
I'm fine.

119
00:05:45,666 --> 00:05:46,433
I will live.

120
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,600
I have nine lives, remember?

121
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:51,033
Then...

122
00:05:51,666 --> 00:05:51,900
Are you

123
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:52,766
thirsty?

124
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:54,533
Hungry? Or...

125
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,366
Do you want anything?

126
00:06:02,566 --> 00:06:03,733
Waking up

127
00:06:04,733 --> 00:06:06,066
and seeing you beside me

128
00:06:07,266 --> 00:06:08,800
is enough.

129
00:06:10,766 --> 00:06:11,500
This is my fault.

130
00:06:13,866 --> 00:06:15,366
I failed to protect you.

131
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,933
You fool.

132
00:06:20,433 --> 00:06:21,533
When it really matters,

133
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,400
you are quite useful.

134
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:26,800
I swear,

135
00:06:29,066 --> 00:06:29,933
from now on,

136
00:06:31,933 --> 00:06:33,600
I will never let you get hurt again.

137
00:06:37,166 --> 00:06:38,266
I went through the account books.

138
00:06:38,566 --> 00:06:40,000
There is nothing concrete.

139
00:06:41,033 --> 00:06:42,600
The court officials listed inside

140
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,500
all used false names.

141
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:44,633
They will never admit to it.

142
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:45,766
If physical evidence is not enough,

143
00:06:46,766 --> 00:06:47,533
we still have witnesses.

144
00:06:49,366 --> 00:06:49,933
You mean

145
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,966
the girls they kidnapped here?

146
00:06:53,266 --> 00:06:53,766
Yes.

147
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,133
Young Master Chang, do you want

148
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,066
some of them to testify as witnesses?

149
00:06:58,433 --> 00:07:00,700
That is our only way
to break through Meizhen House.

150
00:07:06,366 --> 00:07:07,033
Baihu Shen.

151
00:07:09,233 --> 00:07:10,766
I would like to speak with the girls.

152
00:07:19,533 --> 00:07:20,200
Don't be afraid.

153
00:07:20,733 --> 00:07:21,666
You are safe here.

154
00:07:22,533 --> 00:07:22,733
Yes.

155
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,566
Tell us whatever you need.

156
00:07:24,566 --> 00:07:25,933
We want to go home.

157
00:07:28,033 --> 00:07:28,533
Don't worry.

158
00:07:29,266 --> 00:07:30,166
When the case is over,

159
00:07:30,433 --> 00:07:31,433
we will send you home.

160
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:33,633
But the case is not over yet.

161
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:34,833
Is any one of you

162
00:07:35,733 --> 00:07:37,600
willing to testify against Meizhen House?

163
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:43,100
Don't worry.

164
00:07:43,666 --> 00:07:44,766
Whoever is willing to come forward,

165
00:07:45,266 --> 00:07:46,633
I will keep her safe.

166
00:07:51,766 --> 00:07:53,266
Taozi, you tell them.

167
00:07:56,066 --> 00:07:57,433
I don't know anything.

168
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,400
I don't know anything either.

169
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,400
We know nothing.

170
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,400
Nothing.

171
00:08:08,266 --> 00:08:08,766
It's all right.

172
00:08:10,166 --> 00:08:11,233
Go back and think it over.

173
00:08:11,766 --> 00:08:12,266
There is no rush.

174
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:15,633
Let's go.

175
00:08:21,366 --> 00:08:21,933
Xintian.

176
00:08:22,733 --> 00:08:23,833
We don't want to stay here.

177
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:31,566
Move the witnesses?

178
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:32,866
Yes.

179
00:08:33,733 --> 00:08:34,966
The girls are terrified

180
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,433
at staying at the Northern Bureau.

181
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:38,333
I want to move them somewhere else

182
00:08:38,566 --> 00:08:39,466
and have the female Jinyiwei
look after them.

183
00:08:39,666 --> 00:08:40,400
It may help.

184
00:08:41,566 --> 00:08:43,466
Once they feel safe, we can talk to them

185
00:08:44,266 --> 00:08:45,333
and maybe get something out of them.

186
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,266
Do you have a safe place in mind?

187
00:08:47,933 --> 00:08:48,866
Duke Zheng's household

188
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,833
has a secret estate

189
00:08:49,866 --> 00:08:51,066
outside the capital.

190
00:08:52,566 --> 00:08:53,666
Outside the capital?

191
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,433
Where exactly?

192
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,366
Just outside the capital.

193
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:05,566
Bingfan.

194
00:09:06,533 --> 00:09:07,900
So now,

195
00:09:08,566 --> 00:09:09,666
you don't even trust me?

196
00:09:11,166 --> 00:09:12,333
For the witnesses' safety,

197
00:09:12,866 --> 00:09:14,600
the fewer who know, the better.

198
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,366
You will stay here for now.

199
00:09:16,933 --> 00:09:18,700
Chief Squad Leader Cheng
and I will protect you.

200
00:09:19,733 --> 00:09:20,466
From now on,

201
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,933
Constable Guan will bring supplies
every day.

202
00:09:23,666 --> 00:09:24,533
You don't need to go out.

203
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:26,600
If you need anything,

204
00:09:27,266 --> 00:09:29,000
tell me or Chief Squad Leader Cheng.

205
00:09:33,233 --> 00:09:34,000
That was amazing!

206
00:09:34,033 --> 00:09:34,800
Xintian is amazing!

207
00:09:34,833 --> 00:09:36,100
Xintian, you never miss.

208
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:37,733
I will teach you later.

209
00:09:37,933 --> 00:09:39,200
Then no one will be able
to bully you again.

210
00:09:40,066 --> 00:09:41,266
If I learn it,

211
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,433
can I join the Jinyiwei too?

212
00:09:43,933 --> 00:09:45,200
The Jinyiwei?

213
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,400
You want to join the Jinyiwei?

214
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,833
Can girls join too?

215
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:52,266
If I join the Jinyiwei,
no one will dare hurt me again.

216
00:09:52,433 --> 00:09:53,800
We want to join too.

217
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,133
I want to join.

218
00:09:55,166 --> 00:09:56,366
So do we.

219
00:09:57,833 --> 00:09:59,033
As long as you don't look down
on yourselves,

220
00:09:59,166 --> 00:10:00,433
no one can break you so easily.

221
00:10:00,833 --> 00:10:02,166
I know you have suffered.

222
00:10:02,933 --> 00:10:04,366
But if you are willing to testify,

223
00:10:05,166 --> 00:10:05,733
I swear

224
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,933
I will bring down every filthy official

225
00:10:07,933 --> 00:10:09,133
who hurt you

226
00:10:09,333 --> 00:10:10,900
and everyone behind them.

227
00:10:12,366 --> 00:10:13,133
But...

228
00:10:13,433 --> 00:10:14,200
Well...

229
00:10:17,066 --> 00:10:19,000
Taozi, what do you think?

230
00:10:19,066 --> 00:10:21,300
Your people went to Meizhen House
to investigate

231
00:10:21,333 --> 00:10:22,233
and nearly got killed.

232
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,333
Gao Tianxi only got eight years.

233
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:26,266
He was not even an official,

234
00:10:26,566 --> 00:10:27,666
and you still couldn't touch him.

235
00:10:28,266 --> 00:10:30,600
What about those high officials
and nobles?

236
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:31,733
Exactly.

237
00:10:31,733 --> 00:10:33,566
You couldn't even bring down
that beast, Gao Tianxi.

238
00:10:33,733 --> 00:10:35,100
How can you fight those powerful men?

239
00:10:35,566 --> 00:10:36,600
You can't beat them.

240
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,533
Please just let us go home.

241
00:10:38,533 --> 00:10:39,733
Yes, let us go home.

242
00:10:39,733 --> 00:10:41,300
Let us go home.

243
00:10:41,333 --> 00:10:42,166
I want to go home.

244
00:10:42,166 --> 00:10:43,700
Please let us go.

245
00:10:44,333 --> 00:10:45,333
Let us leave.

246
00:10:45,666 --> 00:10:47,233
I don't want to stay here anymore.

247
00:10:53,333 --> 00:10:53,866
Let's go.

248
00:10:54,733 --> 00:10:55,500
We should leave.

249
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:57,800
Let's not get into trouble.

250
00:10:57,833 --> 00:10:58,600
Yes.

251
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,633
Being safe is enough.

252
00:11:01,333 --> 00:11:02,766
We should protect ourselves.

253
00:11:03,333 --> 00:11:03,766
Xintian.

254
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,500
I'm sorry

255
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,433
I couldn't help you.

256
00:11:08,833 --> 00:11:09,866
It is all right, Taozi.

257
00:11:10,566 --> 00:11:11,233
I don't blame you.

258
00:11:11,766 --> 00:11:13,366
Don't worry. None of us will.

259
00:11:14,266 --> 00:11:16,200
I don't want to keep swallowing this.

260
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,200
But I'm scared.

261
00:11:20,366 --> 00:11:21,100
I'm scared that

262
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:23,266
if I tell the truth,

263
00:11:23,266 --> 00:11:24,700
you still won't be able to beat them.

264
00:11:27,266 --> 00:11:27,766
Taozi.

265
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,266
Trust me.

266
00:11:29,733 --> 00:11:31,233
As long as you tell me the truth,

267
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,500
no matter how high his rank is

268
00:11:33,166 --> 00:11:33,900
or how powerful he is,

269
00:11:34,866 --> 00:11:36,266
we will bring him down.

270
00:11:39,433 --> 00:11:42,433
Then, do you dare touch Marquis Taiping?

271
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:00,266
Mr. Zhang.

272
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,833
Why have you brought so many men

273
00:12:02,866 --> 00:12:04,066
into my manor?

274
00:12:04,366 --> 00:12:05,033
Marquis Taiping.

275
00:12:05,733 --> 00:12:06,433
Do you know

276
00:12:07,033 --> 00:12:07,866
this young lady?

277
00:12:09,766 --> 00:12:10,333
No.

278
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,333
Don't be afraid, Taozi.

279
00:12:14,866 --> 00:12:16,766
Today, we settle every debt
and every wrong.

280
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,033
Say it all.

281
00:12:24,766 --> 00:12:25,366
It was him.

282
00:12:26,433 --> 00:12:27,433
When I first came to Meizhen House,

283
00:12:27,433 --> 00:12:28,866
they sent me to serve him.

284
00:12:29,833 --> 00:12:31,200
He raped me.

285
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:32,700
You liar!

286
00:12:33,566 --> 00:12:34,500
Insolent wretch!

287
00:12:34,733 --> 00:12:35,600
Framing a marquis?

288
00:12:35,766 --> 00:12:36,600
Do you know the crime?

289
00:12:39,666 --> 00:12:40,433
Don't be afraid, Taozi.

290
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,700
Say what you need to say.

291
00:12:42,333 --> 00:12:43,433
I have nothing left to lose.

292
00:12:44,366 --> 00:12:44,933
It was him!

293
00:12:46,566 --> 00:12:47,600
What proof do you have?

294
00:12:49,266 --> 00:12:49,700
He...

295
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,233
He has a red birthmark
on his lower back.

296
00:12:58,866 --> 00:12:59,533
Marquis Taiping.

297
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,766
Must I strip you in front of everyone

298
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,066
to verify her claim?

299
00:13:05,566 --> 00:13:06,066
Commander Zhang.

300
00:13:06,233 --> 00:13:08,066
As an imperial official,

301
00:13:08,066 --> 00:13:09,066
you visited brothels

302
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,900
without the slightest shame.

303
00:13:11,066 --> 00:13:13,966
Now you raped an innocent woman
and still dare deny it.

304
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,366
Guards.

305
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,033
Yes!

306
00:13:17,433 --> 00:13:18,866
Take Marquis Taiping, Yin Xian,

307
00:13:19,266 --> 00:13:20,166
to the Imperial Prison

308
00:13:20,433 --> 00:13:21,100
to await judgment!

309
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,200
Who dares?

310
00:13:23,433 --> 00:13:25,100
Get them! Get them!

311
00:13:26,733 --> 00:13:27,166
Take him away.

312
00:13:28,166 --> 00:13:29,833
Mercy! Have mercy!

313
00:13:30,700 --> 00:13:31,533
Mercy!

314
00:13:32,033 --> 00:13:33,200
Have mercy!

315
00:13:57,766 --> 00:14:00,666
(Imperial Edict)

316
00:14:03,366 --> 00:14:06,433
(Fanyang County Office)

317
00:14:07,033 --> 00:14:08,433
Look at the mess you have made for me!

318
00:14:09,366 --> 00:14:10,533
And you still dare complain
about hunger?

319
00:14:13,266 --> 00:14:14,000
Answer me.

320
00:14:15,066 --> 00:14:16,566
The day Meizhen House was sealed,

321
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,266
why did you bring out my golden token?

322
00:14:19,933 --> 00:14:21,533
Were you afraid people wouldn't know

323
00:14:21,566 --> 00:14:23,333
you were connected to me?

324
00:14:23,366 --> 00:14:25,266
I only wanted to use
Your Highness's name

325
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,800
to scare Chang Beiming.

326
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,466
Do you know what has happened

327
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,266
now that everything is exposed?

328
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,933
Our people across the network
are being arrested.

329
00:14:37,366 --> 00:14:38,966
The secret ledgers have all
been destroyed.

330
00:14:39,166 --> 00:14:40,366
But you left witnesses alive.

331
00:14:41,166 --> 00:14:43,333
Those trafficked girls
are coming forward to testify.

332
00:14:44,566 --> 00:14:46,966
Chang Beiming and Zhang Weimin
took this straight to His Majesty.

333
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:47,833
He was furious.

334
00:14:48,066 --> 00:14:49,900
Half the network

335
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:51,933
we spent years building collapsed
overnight.

336
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,833
How could this happen?

337
00:14:54,333 --> 00:14:55,700
Those spineless cowards

338
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,400
will tear each other apart in prison
just to survive.

339
00:15:01,033 --> 00:15:03,800
Our secrets won't stay buried
much longer.

340
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:07,600
Your Highness.

341
00:15:09,066 --> 00:15:10,400
If we kill those witnesses,

342
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,833
the arrested officials can change
their stories together.

343
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,033
Then, Your Highness

344
00:15:15,266 --> 00:15:16,533
can turn the chaos to your advantage.

345
00:15:18,266 --> 00:15:19,800
At least you are not completely useless.

346
00:15:24,866 --> 00:15:27,600
This address came from my spy

347
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,700
inside the Jinyiwei.

348
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,866
(Qingyin Villa, outside the capital)

349
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:33,200
Come. Sit.

350
00:15:39,233 --> 00:15:39,666
Hard day?

351
00:15:46,833 --> 00:15:48,833
I went through four or five offices
today,

352
00:15:49,166 --> 00:15:50,600
arrested seven or eight officials
involved,

353
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:52,533
and nearly worked myself dizzy.

354
00:15:52,566 --> 00:15:53,466
My mouth is dry too.

355
00:15:55,733 --> 00:15:58,266
You look rather pleased.

356
00:15:58,866 --> 00:15:59,733
Of course I am.

357
00:16:00,433 --> 00:16:02,033
This time, we took down Meizhen House
in one move

358
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:03,733
and arrested so many parasites at court.

359
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,133
It felt great.

360
00:16:05,933 --> 00:16:06,933
Then, right now,

361
00:16:07,166 --> 00:16:08,366
you should be out catching criminals.

362
00:16:08,833 --> 00:16:09,866
Why come to Chong'er Pavilion?

363
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,400
To see Hua, of course.

364
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,000
Only Hua?

365
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:18,800
And also,

366
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,733
to see what someone else is doing.

367
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,200
Who is this someone else?

368
00:16:26,433 --> 00:16:27,533
You missed me, didn't you?

369
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,033
Who missed you?

370
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,666
I really came to see Hua.

371
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,066
Young Master! Young Master!

372
00:16:49,733 --> 00:16:50,600
Do you have to

373
00:16:50,866 --> 00:16:53,300
show up at the perfect time every time?

374
00:16:54,266 --> 00:16:54,766
Young Master.

375
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,166
An invitation from Prince Fu's manor.

376
00:16:57,533 --> 00:16:58,100
What?

377
00:17:00,133 --> 00:17:01,133
(Invitation)

378
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:05,333
(To the Heir of Duke Zheng)
Prince Fu has invited me

379
00:17:06,100 --> 00:17:07,100
to his place

380
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:08,766
for a banquet at noon tomorrow.

381
00:17:09,066 --> 00:17:10,666
Don't go. This is a trap.

382
00:17:10,733 --> 00:17:11,566
He is up to no good.

383
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,400
A trap?

384
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:16,200
Even as a prince,

385
00:17:17,266 --> 00:17:19,633
he wouldn't dare openly murder
an imperial official.

386
00:17:20,233 --> 00:17:22,733
This is my chance to meet the man
behind it all.

387
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:37,900
(Prince Fu's Manor)

388
00:17:38,433 --> 00:17:39,200
Young Duke.

389
00:17:42,766 --> 00:17:44,000
You are going to Prince Fu's banquet?

390
00:17:45,166 --> 00:17:45,533
Yes.

391
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,000
After Meizhen House,

392
00:17:47,333 --> 00:17:48,733
Prince Fu will not let this go.

393
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,400
And I owe those girls

394
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:51,800
an answer.

395
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:53,866
But on the way here,

396
00:17:53,933 --> 00:17:54,866
I kept feeling uneasy.

397
00:17:55,866 --> 00:17:56,366
Guan.

398
00:17:57,066 --> 00:17:58,233
No one should know

399
00:17:58,366 --> 00:17:59,300
where Qingyin Villa is, right?

400
00:18:00,033 --> 00:18:01,966
Not many. I'm one of them.

401
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:05,166
Then, could you take some men

402
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:06,966
and check on the villa?

403
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:10,500
Bingfan said that too many people
would draw danger.

404
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:12,166
So watch from a distance.

405
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,766
If all is safe, leave quietly.

406
00:18:13,766 --> 00:18:14,533
If there is danger,

407
00:18:14,833 --> 00:18:16,000
notify me at once.

408
00:18:16,233 --> 00:18:17,833
You think Bingfan and the others
may be in danger?

409
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:20,833
(Prince Fu's Manor)
Prince Fu invited me for no reason.

410
00:18:21,266 --> 00:18:22,300
(Prince Fu's Manor)
I fear he has a scheme.

411
00:18:23,033 --> 00:18:24,033
Right now, it is safer

412
00:18:24,233 --> 00:18:26,433
to overthink than overlook something.

413
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:45,766
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

414
00:18:46,133 --> 00:18:49,500
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

415
00:18:49,766 --> 00:18:52,766
♪My heart drifted lost♪

416
00:18:52,766 --> 00:18:56,166
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

417
00:18:57,266 --> 00:19:00,466
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

418
00:19:00,866 --> 00:19:04,200
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

419
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:07,000
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

420
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:11,033
♪I've softly let it go♪

421
00:19:11,033 --> 00:19:14,900
♪The vow you made was true♪

422
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:18,633
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

423
00:19:18,966 --> 00:19:20,866
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

424
00:19:20,866 --> 00:19:25,400
♪And forget at world's end♪

425
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:27,200
♪Embracing memory♪

426
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:29,566
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

427
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:33,466
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

428
00:19:33,466 --> 00:19:35,766
♪I wish to let it pass♪

429
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:40,800
♪And run toward this vast life♪

